OL,3,CAsylum seeker recalls hiding inside
OL,4,Cbesieged hotel during summer riots
OL,6,FFaustin Karake, known to his friends
OL,7,Fas Eric, fled the Democratic Republic
OL,8,Fof Congo in 2010 after his mother and
OL,9,Ffather were murdered in their home
OL,10,Fduring civil unrest.
OL,12,FNow, 15 years on, he continues to live
OL,13,Fin limbo awaiting asylum - unable to
OL,14,Fwork, get a home or settle into life
OL,15,Fin the UK.
OL,17,FHe attempted to build a life for
OL,18,Fhimself in Plymouth before he was told
OL,19,Fhe would have to move elsewhere in the
OL,20,Fcountry.
