OL,3,CAsylum seeker recalls hiding inside
OL,4,Cbesieged hotel during summer riots
OL,6,FOn the evening of 4 August, the asylum
OL,7,Fhotel in Tamworth where Eric was being
OL,8,Fhoused was targeted by anti-
OL,9,Fimmigration protestors.
OL,11,FA mob launched rocks, fireworks and
OL,12,Fpetrol bombs at the windows of the
OL,13,Fhotel which had 180 asylum seekers
OL,14,Finside.
OL,16,FIn an interview with ITV News West
OL,17,FCountry Eric, who has now been
OL,18,Frehoused in Oxford, recalls the night
OL,19,Fhe, and his fellow asylum seekers,
OL,20,Ffeared they might die.
