OL,3,CAsylum seeker recalls hiding inside
OL,4,Cbesieged hotel during summer riots
OL,6,F"Inside (the hotel) we've got some
OL,7,Fpeople that look after us. So they
OL,8,Ftold us before what (was happening).
OL,10,F"They come to tell us - if anything
OL,11,Fgoing to happen here just be quiet,
OL,12,Fdon't be scared, don't shout, don't
OL,13,Fcome out of the house, you need to
OL,14,Fstay inside.
OL,16,F"Loads of (protestors came), loads of
OL,17,Fpeople was angry, they come with many
OL,18,Fthings.
