OL,3,CAsylum seeker recalls hiding inside
OL,4,Cbesieged hotel during summer riots
OL,6,F"(They were) shouting, banging doors,
OL,7,Fthrowing stones on the walls, the
OL,8,Fdoors, the window.
OL,10,F"It was scary. It was really very,
OL,11,Fvery, scary.
OL,13,F"When you're in that situation you've
OL,14,Fno option - you have to stay quiet and
OL,15,Fwait (to see) what is going to happen.
OL,16,FIt was very scary.
OL,18,F"I was scared. I was scared in case,
OL,19,Fif they're going to come in we're
OL,20,Fgoing to get killed or something.
