OL,3,CAsylum seeker recalls hiding inside
OL,4,Cbesieged hotel during summer riots
OL,6,F"It was dangerous. You had to pray,
OL,7,Fput my knee down and pray, ask God to
OL,8,Fhelp me and that's it.
OL,10,F"I was praying for my life. Praying
OL,11,Ffor the whole hotel as well. I
OL,12,Fencouraged people to pray - I tell
OL,13,Fpeople pray if you Muslim, pray if you
OL,14,FChristian, pray, you need to pray, we
OL,15,Fneed help from God as we can't do
OL,16,Fnothing.
OL,18,F"You could die you know, you could die
OL,19,Feasily, because people were very
OL,20,Fangry, very, very, very angry.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUzD@AOU
