OL,3,CAsylum seeker recalls hiding inside
OL,4,Cbesieged hotel during summer riots
OL,6,F"The police were involved, so they
OL,7,Ftried to do their best.
OL,9,F"You can't say nothing (to the
OL,10,Fprotestors). Everything you say
OL,11,Fthey're going to argue with, they're
OL,12,Fnot going to accept it. By myself I
OL,13,Fcan't do nothing.
OL,15,F"If the government can teach people
OL,16,Fhow to love each other, to accept
OL,17,Fanything, change can happen.
OL,19,F"It's not everybody - you cannot blame
OL,20,Fa whole country.
